{"tid":527414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【狗咬狗】小蝗車 ofo 否認現金短缺 指責騰訊造假新聞","createTime":"2018-01-12T15:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T15:32:05.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3db5308c3b552fb9895766ff43350ef99a2ed3be","tid":527414,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180112/s00002/2bb533c890e18934dfd288548c6c6678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180112%2Fs00002%2F2bb533c890e18934dfd288548c6c6678.jpg&h=0ed9276e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那共享單車ofo今日被指手頭現金短缺，該公司晚上發出聲明，強調目前訂單量保持穩定，資金流非常健康。<br />\n<br />\n今早，《騰訊科技》報道指，ofo的可用資金不到6億元人民幣，僅能維持一個月，同時欠供應商約25億元人民幣及虧空按金總額約30億元人民幣。報道並指，ofo目前的每日訂單數已下降至約1000萬。"},{"pid":"aac76ff0c88ce767b185728128aa4d7e009ea837","tid":527414,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}